    <title>头文件循环依赖问题的解决：</title>
    <url>/2023/04/23/include-file-problem/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="2023-04-22"><a href="#2023-04-22" class="headerlink" title="2023.04.22"></a>2023.04.22</h1><h2 id="深入理解C项目头文件循环依赖问题"><a href="#深入理解C项目头文件循环依赖问题" class="headerlink" title="深入理解C项目头文件循环依赖问题"></a>深入理解C项目头文件循环依赖问题</h2><h3 id="1-gt-首先来看看头文件的相互引用"><a href="#1-gt-首先来看看头文件的相互引用" class="headerlink" title="1&gt;首先来看看头文件的相互引用"></a>1&gt;首先来看看头文件的相互引用</h3><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">/*this is interrupt.h*/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&quot;memory.h&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//definations</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//--------------------------------</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/*this is memory.h*/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&quot;interrupt.h&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//definations</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//--------------------------------</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/*this is page_fault.c*/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">page_fault_handler</span><span class="params">(... , ...)</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//code</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>


<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//尝试编译报错</span></span><br><span class="line">error: <span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> nested too deeply</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p> 这是由于预处理阶段，两个头文件相互嵌套，导致头文件展开无限循环。</p>
<h6 id="解决方法："><a href="#解决方法：" class="headerlink" title="解决方法："></a>解决方法：</h6><h4 id="1-使用ifndef方式："><a href="#1-使用ifndef方式：" class="headerlink" title="(1)使用ifndef方式："></a>(1)使用ifndef方式：</h4> <figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"> <span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">ifndef</span>  __SOMEFILE_H__</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span>   __SOMEFILE_H__</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"> ... ... <span class="comment">// 声明、定义语句</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">endif</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p> #ifndef的方式可以保证同一文件不会被包含多次，也能保证内容完全相同的两个文件不会被同时包含。需要注意不同文件中的__SOMEFILE_H__宏命名不能相同。</p>
<h3 id="2-gt-我们再来来看循环依赖问题如何解决？"><a href="#2-gt-我们再来来看循环依赖问题如何解决？" class="headerlink" title="2&gt;我们再来来看循环依赖问题如何解决？"></a>2&gt;我们再来来看循环依赖问题如何解决？</h3><p>错误代码：</p>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//this is A.h</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">ifndef</span> A_H</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> A_H</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&quot;B.h&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">A</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">typedef</span> vector&lt;string&gt;::size_type size_type;</span><br><span class="line">    B b;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">endif</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>


<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//this is B.h</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">ifndef</span> B_H</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> B_H</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&quot;A.h&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">B</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    A::size_type num;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">endif</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//在B头文件中 A::的地方会有编译错误</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//error: use of undeclared identifier &#x27;A&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//A::size_type num;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>方法 1. 编码技巧。使用前置声明 (forward declaration)[4]，其它回答已述，这里不赘述。原理是编译器核算指针时，它的 size 是固定值，不用看它指向的 class 的实现。但是核算 class 及其对象的 size 时，就必需看 class 的实现了。由此也衍生出一个惯用法——pImpl[3]，其可以作为以下重新设计程序结构时的实现方法。</p>
<p>方法2：重新设计程序结构。遵循面向对象设计的 SOLID[5] 原则中的「接口隔离原则」和「依赖倒置原则」。当看到这种循环依赖结构，直觉就该告诉你，需要把一些东西抽象为接口。接口是一种约定形式，具体可以是函数签名（包括传统的函数指针及现代的 callable object）、抽象类、模板，甚至某种设计模式（如迭代器、观察者、发布-订阅模式等）。接口的目的是为了隔离变化。以本题为例，为什么 class A 里要内含 class B 成员呢？究其根本是要利用 class B 的行为。那么现在可以抽象出一个接口 class IB，一个抽象类，class B 是它的实现之一。因此 class A 和 class B 现在都依赖 class IB了，循环依赖便消除了。</p>
<p>方法二的改进代码如下所示：</p>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// this is IB.h</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">ifndef</span> IB_H</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> IB_H</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;vector&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;string&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">IB</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">typedef</span> vector&lt;string&gt;::size_type size_type;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">virtual</span> ~<span class="built_in">IB</span>() &#123;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">virtual</span> size_type <span class="title">get_num</span><span class="params">()</span> <span class="type">const</span> </span>= <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//实现类必须实现抽象类中的所有纯虚函数，否则实现类也将成为抽象类。</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">endif</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// this is B.h</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">ifndef</span> B_H</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> B_H</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&quot;IB.h&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">B</span>: <span class="keyword">public</span> IB &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function">size_type <span class="title">get_num</span><span class="params">()</span> <span class="type">const</span> </span>&#123; <span class="keyword">return</span> num; &#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">private</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    size_type num;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">endif</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// this is A.h</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">ifndef</span> A_H</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> A_H</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&quot;IB.h&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">A</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">A</span>(IB* ib): <span class="built_in">b</span>(ib) &#123;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function">size_type <span class="title">get_num</span><span class="params">()</span> <span class="type">const</span> </span>&#123; <span class="keyword">return</span> b-&gt;<span class="built_in">get_num</span>(); &#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">private</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    IB* b;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">endif</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>**<br>这段代码实现了一个简单的接口隔离设计模式，遵循了 SOLID 设计原则中的「接口隔离原则」和「依赖倒置原则」。主要实现了以下几个类：</p>
<p>IB：抽象类，定义了一个纯虚函数 get_num()，用于获取一个 size_type 类型的数值。通过虚函数和纯虚函数实现了接口抽象。</p>
<p>B：实现了 IB 接口，实现了 get_num() 函数。</p>
<p>A：包含了一个 IB 类型的成员变量 b，通过构造函数将 b 的值初始化为传入的 IB 类型指针。A 类实现了一个成员函数 get_num()，调用 b 的 get_num() 函数获取一个 size_type 类型的数值。</p>
<p>整体的实现思路是，将 IB 接口作为 B 的基类，并在 B 中实现接口的纯虚函数。A 类中成员变量 b 为 IB 类型的指针，在构造函数中将其初始化为传入的 IB 类型指针，A 类中的成员函数 get_num() 调用 b 的 get_num() 函数，实现了通过接口隔离和依赖倒置来避免循环依赖问题。<br>**</p>
<h3 id="再来看一个更加直观的例子：："><a href="#再来看一个更加直观的例子：：" class="headerlink" title="再来看一个更加直观的例子：："></a>再来看一个更加直观的例子：：</h3><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// A.h</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">ifndef</span> A_H</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> A_H</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&quot;B.h&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">A</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    B b;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">do_something</span><span class="params">()</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">endif</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// B.h</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">ifndef</span> B_H</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> B_H</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&quot;A.h&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">B</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    A a;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">do_something</span><span class="params">()</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">endif</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>使用接口隔离技术消除头文件循环依赖！</p>
<p>相当于把依赖对方的某一种行为抽象成一个接口类</p>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// IB.h</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">ifndef</span> IB_H</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> IB_H</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">IB</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">virtual</span> ~<span class="built_in">IB</span>() &#123;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">virtual</span> <span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">do_something</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>= <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">endif</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// IA.h</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">ifndef</span> IA_H</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> IA_H</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">IA</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">virtual</span> <span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">do_something</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>= <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">endif</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// A.h</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">ifndef</span> A_H</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> A_H</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&quot;IB.h&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">A</span> : <span class="keyword">public</span> IA&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">do_something</span><span class="params">()</span> <span class="keyword">override</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">    IB* b;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">endif</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// B.h</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">ifndef</span> B_H</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> B_H</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&quot;IA.h&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">B</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">do_something</span><span class="params">()</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">    IA* a;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">endif</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
